title: Jet Fighter Airplane Racing
description: Jet Fighter Airplane Racing is an action airplane game where you can complete many different missions, improve your flying skills, and become a true professional in piloting! There are many exclusive airplanes available, such as MiG-21 “Fishbed", McDonnell Douglas F-4 Phantom II, MiG-29 “Fulcrum”, F-16 Fighting Falcon, MiG-31 BM “Foxhound”, F-22 Raptor, SU-35 “Flanker-E”, SU-47 "Firkin", SU-57. Become a skilled fighter pilot in the sky and get lots of adrenaline. Avoid the fly traffic in jet-flying race games! Are you ready for a traffic airplane adventure? Fasten your seatbelt and prepare to fly!
